me, in Word- press and Drupal, meanwhile working on optimise existing sites to achieve greater visibility.\r\nStarting from learning Wordpress / Drupal, I had the needs to also deepen complementary fields such as web-hosting and marketing, while keeping an eye on new HTML5 technologies and responsive layout, which allows applications to be accessible from most devic- es, such as TV, PC and smartphones.\r\nComing from a highly interdisciplinary background, I have good at- titude to work on projects that normally require several professionals: for instance I may design a 3D model from basic product data, then move on marketing the product through developing a company website, deploying strategies to drive more traffic with social, SEO and email targets. Marketing materials aren’t limited to digital, they come together with printed brochures for new and old customers; that’s my view.','Profile','','inherit','open','open','','9-revision-8','','','2012-10-15 13:02:28','2012-10-15 13:02:28','',9,'http://localhost/wp-portfolio/?p=388',0,'revision','',0),(389,1,'2013-01-17 00:25:59','2013-01-17 00:25:59',' ','','','publish','open','open','','389','','','2013-01-17 22:52:49','2013-01-17 22:52:49','',0,'http://localhost/wp-portfolio/?p=389',4,'nav_menu_item','',0),(393,1,'2013-01-17 21:24:48','2013-01-17 21:24:48','A seguito di una sostanziale esperienza in ricerca & sviluppo di prodotti per la produzione industriale, ho intrapreso una carriera in am- bito Web, interessato soprattutto da CMS e possibilità di creare vere e proprie applicazioni, piuttosto che pagine statiche e obsolete. Ad oggi seguo la gestione di alcuni siti Web sviluppati da me, in Wordpress, Drupal e mi occupo di ottimizzare siti già esistenti per rag- giungere maggiore visibilità.\r\nPartendo dallo studio di Wordpress/Drupal ho avuto la necessità di approfondire anche ambiti complementari come hosting e web- marketing, tenendo sempre viva l’ attenzione sulle nuove tecnologie HTML5 e layout dinamico che per