=\"http://video.ted.com/assets/player/swf/EmbedPlayer.swf\" wmode=\"transparent\" type=\"application/x-shockwave-flash\" allowscriptaccess=\"always\" height=\"355\" flashvars=\"vu=http://video.ted.com/talk/stream/2007/Blank/DavidGallo_2007-320k.mp4&amp;su=http://images.ted.com/images/ted/tedindex/embed-posters/DavidGallo-2007.embed_thumbnail.jpg&amp;vw=512&amp;vh=288&amp;ap=0&amp;ti=206&amp;lang=en&amp;introDuration=15330&amp;adDuration=4000&amp;postAdDuration=830&amp;adKeys=talk=david_gallo_shows_underwater_astonishments;year=2007;theme=evolution_s_genius;theme=animals_that_amaze;theme=ocean_stories;theme=inspired_by_nature;event=TED2007;tag=animals;tag=evolution;tag=exploration;tag=fish;tag=oceans;tag=science;tag=short+talk;tag=technology;&amp;preAdTag=tconf.ted/embed;tile=1;sz=512x288;\" width=\"500\"></embed></object>\n\n<blockquote><div>\n					<p>David Gallo shows jaw-dropping footage of amazing sea creatures, including a color-shifting cuttlefish, a perfectly camouflaged octopus, and a Times Square\'s worth of neon light displays from fish who live in the blackest depths of the ocean.</p>\n											<p>\n							A pioneer in ocean exploration, David Gallo is an enthusiastic ambassador between the sea and those of us on dry land. <a href=\"http://www.ted.com/talks/lang/en/david_gallo_shows_underwater_astonishments.html#\" title=\"David Gallo\'s bio\" target=\"_blank\">Full bio »</a>						</p>\n					\n											<p>\n									</p></div></blockquote><div class=\"posterous_quote_citation\">via <a href=\"http://www.ted.com/talks/lang/en/david_gallo_shows_underwater_astonishments.html\">ted.com</a></div>\n    <p></p></div>\n  ','David Gallo: Underwater astonishments','','publish','open','open','','david-gallo-underwater-astonishments','','','2012-08-28 22:11:00','2012-08-28 22:11:00','',0,'http://ale.2hire.us/david-gallo-underwater-astonishments/',0,'post','',0),(418,1,'2012-08-27 12:31:00','2012-08-27 12:31:00','\n    <div class=\"posterous_bookmarklet_entry\">\n  